commit.title: [coqtop] Tweak API to avoid abstraction breakage.
commit.message:
[coqtop] Tweak API to avoid abstraction breakage.

We provide a principled mechanism to mask all feeders in favor of an
concrete one. This allows to clean up the use of different feeders in
`coqtop`, in particular it avoids having to leak feeder ids to
miscellaneous subroutines.
